<TEXT>
<P>
I'd like to call attention to an underrated actor, Joe Penny. In movies from 
"Deathmoon" to "The Operation," from guest-starring roles in "Vega$" and "Matt 
Houston" to co-starring roles in "Riptide" and "Jake and the Fatman," he has 
proven himself a versatile and accomplished actor. Some roles may not have been 
the choicest but that has never seemed to tarnish his passion for giving it his 
best. 
</P>
<P>
Sheila R. McGee, Nipomo 
</P>
