PRESIDENTS' DAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Monday is Presidents' Day, created to celebrate George Washington's and Abraham 
Lincoln's birthdays. 
</P>
<P>
OPEN: Most stores and the Los Angeles Law Library. Rapid Transit District buses 
will follow regular schedules. 
</P>
<P>
