treasure trove of books. ; Photo, Author Lion Feuchtwanger's mansion was a 
gathering place for intellectuals and artists. . . . letter from Thomas Mann. ; 
Photo, . . . The house was toured recently by Prof. Harold von Hofe. Biography 
below includes a LISA ROMEREIN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Thomas Mann ; Photo, 
Bertolt Brecht ; Photo, Aldous Huxley 
</P>
