auto body shop business in La Puente with SBA loan guarantee. TONY BARNARD / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, Willy and Richard Guldstrand purchased their 
automotive engineering facility in Culver City with SBA financing through a 
private lender. JAMES RUEBSAMEN 
</P>
