Asok Boopathy and Tom Reidy will meet in today's 2:20 p.m. final of the 38th 
Dave Freeman Open at Balboa Park. Boopathy defeated Arifan Wiguna in the 
semifinals and Reidy beat Marc Padre. 
</P>
<P>
RUGBY 
</P>
