<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 12; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
67 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD IN BRIEF; 
</P>
<P>
