the Pacific Northwest, while the Southeast cleaned up from a wave of 
thunderstorms and tornadoes that killed two people and sent hundreds fleeing 
from their homes. Above, a house in Kentucky's southeastern Jefferson County is 
surrounded by floodwaters. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
