family. ; Photo, Douglas Haines paints under the approving eye of instructor 
Gail Tomura. ALEXANDER GALLARDO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Jonde Northcutt, 
left, and Nick Capaci conduct monotype (printmaking, painting and drawing) 
workshops at the women's prison. AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times; 
